column19: This video describes a young boy named David in the backseat of his car after getting out of the dentist's office. His father, who is sitting in the front seat, is recording him asking questions about David's experience.
David sits up from his seat, pointing two fingers in the air.
David puts his back to his seat and gets his right index finger and puts it in his mouth, which is now open.
His father stops him from putting it into his mouth.
David shakes his head around stating he cannot see anything.
David tries to get up from his seat putting both hands down pushing himself up yelling.
David gets his right index finger and points it towards his teeth asking his father questions.
David lifts up his head and asks his father questions while putting both hands in the air.
David leans his head forward as his father laughs and pans the camera towards the left, ending the video.
